# AddProject.skill

Repo-local entrypoint for the reusable Codex skill that imports a local project folder into this portfolio.

Canonical skill file:

```text
skills/add-project/SKILL.md
```

Use this by saying something like:

```text
使用 AddProject.skill，把 D:\path\to\new_project 部署成一个新项目
```

The skill covers branch creation, local source-folder audit, public-safe asset curation, bilingual notes, project page creation, media entries, review, verification, GitHub pushes at each milestone, and `/neat`-style handoff docs.
